latestIgtvVideos.title: Introducing Kastoor’s Sniff Samples
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Have been wanting to know the scent of all our modern ittars?

Ittars, by the nature of being pure and without alcohol, lasts for multiple days on a piece of cloth. So we thought why not make that a medium for you to get to know your favourite Kastoor scents. 

It’s not just any cloth, but the highly sustainable bamboo stain which is also highly absorbent for the scent to last for days. 

Sniff Samples are complimentary with any Kastoor buy. If you want them without Kastoor’s full 8ml bottle, they are available at a minimum cost. 

Enjoy sniffing your favourite Kastoor, we are sure we will have you back for more 💛 We have been experimenting by keeping it in purse/wallet or under pillow and it truly does elevate your mood. 

The pieces are entirely sanitised and handled with utmost hygiene and care. 

DM to enquire.

A day as a Banarasi ! The fluid rich tapestry of Kashi that weaves together abandoned moments of silence and spirituality. The art of witnessing life dancing to the surreal flow of Ganga. A Banarasi knows how to live life just by watching Ganga in its splendour, its crests and troughs, its creases and folds. 

Albeli Ganga. 
Matwalj Ganga.
Har Har Ganga. 
Ghar Ghar Ganga.

Welcome to the world of Banaras. 

The Air of Banaras - as fluid as it can be, the richest elixir, the most ethereal blend. 

Bringing you the essence of Banaras to your home with @kastoor.co ‘s very first range of spatial scents.

latestPosts.caption: Slur and slumber season is here ! Happy Thursday, you all! The brain fog is real. We got this, I guess!

It was a pleasure to be on the panel of IIT Hyderabad to speak on Entrepreneurship & Sustainablity. Honoured to share the stage with some of my favorite founders with a vision and interact with the students nourishing their dreams. 

Our chat went much beyond Entrepreneurship & Sustainability to life anecdotes on courage, grit, determination spilling through even lunch. As a first-generation entrepreneur, my word is clear - there is no blueprint to Entrepreneurship. I see it as such a boon because I get the freedom to think what’s not been thought. At the core of it, you should be dedicated to having fun with what you create, be attached to the problem not the product and be obsessed with the customer experience. 

Thank you @iithyderabad @ecell_iith for having me and your beautiful hospitality. And to all the students,  thanks for meeting me with such warmth. I remember you with fond tenderness.
